title: SVENGOOLIE The Mummy's Ghost (1944) Chaney / Carradine 12-31-16
description:
Chicago's Svengoolie Presents: The Mummy's Ghost, the Fourth film in the Universal series, and the 2nd to Feature Lon Chaney Jr. as Kharis. Also stars John Carradine, George Zucco and Ramsay Ames.

It was filmed from August 23-September 1, 1943, but not released until June 30, 1944 (copyrighted 1943). The final film in this series (The Mummy's Curse) was released 6 months later in December of the same year.

I used a DVD print of the film with the Svengoolie segments edited in appropriately ( better picture quality for the film) and the original Air Date for this recording was 12-31-2016.

Enjoy and requests are Welcome !! Unfortunately, Pirate Bay doesn't have a notification system for messages, so yours may go unread for some time. I'll try my best to keep up.

whodude33

PS: Next up is Svengoolie - "The Mummy's Curse" , the final Lon Chaney Jr. Mummy film and in a few days, "Tarantulas : The Deadly Cargo" by request
